26:47.930 --> 26:53.260
Nou, de man in Ludwigsburg,

26:53.260 --> 26:53.460
Ja.

26:53.460 --> 26:55.430
hoe heet die, Walther.

26:55.430 --> 26:55.430
Ja.

26:55.430 --> 26:58.180
