27:49.780 --> 27:49.810
[hoest]

27:49.810 --> 27:52.600
even los van Demjanjuk, die eerste transporten.

27:52.600 --> 27:53.010
Ja.

27:53.010 --> 27:54.300
Dus tot eind maart.

27:54.300 --> 27:55.570
Ja.

27:55.780 --> 28:01.510
